rows.label: qst502014_msg0001
rows.name: Um...is something the matter here?

rows.label: qst502014_msg0002
rows.name:
Ookiooki just arrive here at Liberalitas
islands. Tour guide Sulala here was
meant to showing Ookiooki around.

rows.label: qst502014_msg0003
rows.name:
But Sulala get even more excity than
Ookiooki! Sulala slip and hit head!

rows.label: qst502014_msg0005
rows.name:
Well, that's not good at all!
I'll go fetch a doctor.

rows.label: qst502014_msg0006
rows.name:
Wait please! Too late now for doctor!
Sulala heart already stop beating!

rows.label: qst502014_msg0007
rows.name:
Could friend use lightning power to
start heart of Sulala again?!

rows.label: qst502014_msg0008
rows.name: Whaaaaa?!

rows.label: qst502014_msg0009
rows.name:
Is no time for hesitate!
Every second, life of Sulala is slip away!

rows.label: qst502014_msg0010
rows.name:
Oohhhhhh...
I guess I'll just have to try!

rows.label: qst502014_msg0011
rows.name: Meh-meh-meh!!!

rows.label: qst502014_msg0012
rows.name: Big success!

rows.label: qst502014_msg0013
rows.name:
Whew-whew! Sulala get so excity
there, felt like caught a glimpse of
Elysium for a moment!

rows.label: qst502014_msg0014
rows.name:
Now, where was we? Come along
Ookiooki, lots to see in Liberalitas!

rows.label: qst502014_msg0015
rows.name: Wait one moment!

rows.label: qst502014_msg0016
rows.name:
Sulala must saying thank you
to this nice person.

rows.label: qst502014_msg0017
rows.name: Saying thank you?

rows.label: qst502014_msg0018
rows.name:
Sulala not really understand,
but thank you friend!

rows.label: qst502014_msg0019
rows.name:
Ummm... That's OK.
Just as long as you're all right.

rows.label: qst502014_msg0020
rows.name:
Friend is savior of life of Sulala!
Thank you friend!

rows.label: qst502014_msg0021
rows.name:
It looks like I just don't have
the power to do this...

rows.label: qst502014_msg0022
rows.name: I'm so sorry!
